text: Théodore Nzue Nguema (9 November 1973 – 5 May 2022) was a Gabonese football manager and professional player. He played as a striker. He played for the Gabon national team between 1995 and 2005, making 77 appearances. Nguema died on 5 May 2022 in Mongomo, Equatorial Guinea at the age of 48. ==References== ==Other websites== * * Category:1973 births Category:2022 deaths Category:Gabonese people Category:African footballers
